abstract: Miami Dolphins general manager Dennis Hickey steps down after two years with team.

headline.print_headline: Dolphins Part Ways With General Manager
headline.main: Dolphins Part Ways With General Manager

snippet: General Manager Dennis Hickey has parted ways with the Miami Dolphins at the end of a disappointing season.
